to the Crown Prince.

122
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:37,039
What should I do?

123
00:10:37,840 --> 00:10:39,320
Are you sure?

124
00:10:39,320 --> 00:10:40,519
L-Lord Sun,

125
00:10:40,519 --> 00:10:42,840
