127
00:10:47,679 --> 00:10:50,559
My lord, a seventh-rank will do.

128
00:10:52,000 --> 00:10:54,960
Eighth-rank, eighth-rank will also do, my lord.

129
00:10:55,600 --> 00:10:58,679
Your Highness, do we need to call
the imperial physician?

130
00:10:58,679 --> 00:11:00,808
It doesn't matter.

131
00:11:02,000 --> 00:11:04,399
You go take a look at the Wen Residence.

132
00:11:04,399 --> 00:11:06,320
I don't know why…

133
00:11:06,320 --> 00:11:08,879
I feel uneasy today.

134
00:11:09,480 --> 00:11:11,720
Lady Wen of the county

135
00:11:11,720 --> 00:11:14,152
is going to be the Crown Princess.

136
00:11:15,480 --> 00:11:17,544
Your Highness!

137
00:11:19,720 --> 00:11:21,559
What did you say?

138
00:11:21,559 --> 00:11:23,080
It's all my fault.

139
00:11:23,080 --> 00:11:25,399
That day, Lady Wen let me lead the Crown Prince
away from the Eastern Palace,

140
00:11:25,399 --> 00:11:27,120
