to find someone.

141
00:11:27,120 --> 00:11:30,639
But she was detained by the Crown Prince.

142
00:11:30,639 --> 00:11:33,320
If it is really so,

143
00:11:34,159 --> 00:11:36,559
then Wan is

144
00:11:37,240 --> 00:11:39,559
